"><a href=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/\" class=\"bl\" target=\"_blank\">企業サイトはこちら<img src=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/images/icon-link-white.svg\" alt=\"リンク\"></a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"footer-section2\">\n      <div class=\"inner content1350\">\n        <div id=\"footer-copyright-table\" class=\"inblock-wrap content1124\">\n          <div class=\"footer-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/privacy/\" class=\"bl\" target=\"_blank\">プライバシー・ポリシー</a></div>\n          <div class=\"footer-btn\"><a href=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/sitepolicy/\" class=\"footer-btn bl\" target=\"_blank\">サイトポリシー</a></div>\n          <div class=\"copyright-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"copyright\">Copyright &copy; KAWAKITA ELECTRICAL CONSTRUCTION ENGINEERING CO., LTD. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n  <div id=\"pagetop\" class=\"pic\"><a href=\"#main\" class=\"bl smooth\"><img src=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/images/pagetop.png\" alt=\"PAGE TOP\"></a></div>\n  <script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\n    <script src=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/plugins/slick/slick.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/js/common.js\"></script>\n  </body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.kawakita.co.jp/recruit/interview/ishiguro/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T16:44:15.058Z"}